	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["Temperature was determined by fitting of measured"
		,"neutron spectrum by Maxwellian distribution in energy"
		,"range 0.7 - 10 MeV."
		," Measured at 0.010 - 10 MeV energy range spectrum is"
		,"presented on Fig. (low quality for digitization) of"
		,"page 141 in R,INDC(CCP)-060,139,1974."]
	}
      ]
     ,"COMMENT":[
	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["Of authors."
		," At energy range below 0.7 MeV the measured spectrum"
		,"is higher than Maxwellian due to delayed neutrons."]
	}
